{"TopicId":186822,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"More flexible control over savegame type when creating new","CreatedByName":"CaveJohnson376","CreatedById":180382,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-07-29T18:07:58Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"CaveJohnson376","CreatedById":180382,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-07-29T18:07:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt would be cool to enable or disable specific aspects of game, like science tree, capitalism, missions, building upgrade, etc when creating new savegame.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-07-31T06:20:12Z\u0022 title=\u002207/31/2019 06:20  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 31, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by CaveJohnson376\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Aziz","CreatedById":150811,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-07-30T05:36:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlt\u002BF12? Few clicks and you max out - as in disable - whichever aspect of career you want.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"CaveJohnson376","CreatedById":180382,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-07-30T08:36:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223643144\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022186822\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221564464980\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022150811\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022The Aziz\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, The Aziz said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlt\u002BF12? Few clicks and you max out - as in disable\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E - whichever aspect of career you want.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIts a solution, too\u003Cbr\u003E\nBut it would be cool to toggle anything when creating savegame, not when it created.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jimmidii","CreatedById":9293,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-07-30T12:21:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223643193\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022186822\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221564475780\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022180382\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022CaveJohnson376\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 hours ago, CaveJohnson376 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIts a solution, too\u003Cbr\u003E\nBut it would be cool to toggle anything when creating savegame, not when it created.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can change starting values when creating a new save (for example, giving yourself enough funds and science to max out the research centre and research tree)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"CaveJohnson376","CreatedById":180382,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-07-30T13:04:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223643257\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022186822\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221564489310\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u00229293\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Jimmidii\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n41 minutes ago, Jimmidii said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can change starting values when creating a new save (for example, giving yourself enough funds and science to max out the research centre and research tree)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut it doesnt completely removes game\u00A0mechanics\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Wjolcz","CreatedById":39636,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-07-30T23:05:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223642888\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022186822\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221564423679\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022180382\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022CaveJohnson376\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 7/29/2019 at 8:07 PM, CaveJohnson376 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt would be cool to enable or disable specific aspects of game, like science tree, capitalism, missions, building upgrade, etc.\u003Cbr\u003E\nIs\u0027nt it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes. I\u0027m really fed up with science points as tech currency. I too wish I could disable it and use funds to research the tree instead.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u002239636\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed6157399227\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/174560-add-a-fourth-game-mode/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:213px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-07-30T23:07:08Z\u0022 title=\u002207/30/2019 11:07  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00224 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 30, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by Wjolcz\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"CaveJohnson376","CreatedById":180382,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-07-31T07:21:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223643527\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022186822\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221564527905\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002239636\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Wjolcz\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 hours ago, Wjolcz said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes. I\u0027m really fed up with science points as tech currency. I too wish I could disable \u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003Eit and use funds to\u003Cspan\u003E\uFEFF\u003C/span\u003E research the tree instead.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedauthorid=\u002239636\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed462761645\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/174560-add-a-fourth-game-mode/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:209px;max-width:500px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut being able to disable on enable specific aspects in the savegame is better anyways, isnt it? Also, as i think, its easier to code.\u003Cbr\u003E\nOh, also these three savegame types can be left as savegame settings presets\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}